data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a BRAND NEW ROOF & A 5 YEAR TRANSFERABLE WARRANTY located on the desirable northeast side of town. This well-maintained residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and outdoor enjoyment. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open living room with ample natural light, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends. The kitchen is equipped with contemporary appliances and plenty of counter space. Once you step outside you'll discover this property is fully fenced, ensuring privacy and security for your loved ones and pets to roam and play freely, while lounging under the covered patio, and having those summer barbecues. This home is the ideal combination of indoor comfort and outdoor fun, making it the perfect place to call home for families or those who love to entertain. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property yours and start creating lasting memories in this delightful oasis.
